## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online resources, which may not encompass all perspectives or the latest research developments. Additionally, the definitions and applications of these terms can vary across different healthcare settings and cultural contexts, which may not be fully captured in the sources reviewed. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of these concepts in practice.